# --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# machine_learning working-storage + heavyweight artifacts. NEVER commit bulk data,
# model weights, checkpoints, or caches. The repository holds only code, config,
# registry, schemas, small fixtures, manifests summaries, reports, and docs.
#
# NOTE: the *repository-root* .gitignore already ignores `data/` and `*.parquet`, which
# covers machine_learning/data/. This file adds ML-specific ignores and is explicit so
# the intent is obvious to a human auditor reading only this directory.
# --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

# Bulk working storage (raw downloads, normalized shards, examples, splits, generated manifests)
data/raw/
data/normalized/
data/examples/
data/splits/
data/manifests/
data/samples/
data/cache/
data/logs/
data/state/

# Model weights, adapters, checkpoints, quantized exports
*.safetensors
*.bin
*.pt
*.gguf
artifacts/checkpoints/
artifacts/adapters/
artifacts/runs/
artifacts/merged/

# HF + torch caches if they land locally
.hf_cache/
hf_home/
*.arrow
*.lock

# Columnar/temp data formats anywhere under this tree
*.parquet
*.feather
*.tmp
*.partial
*.download

# But DO keep committed structure markers, small fixtures, committed manifest summaries
!tests/fixtures/**
!artifacts/manifests/**
!reports/**
